		</table></td><td class="PanelBody" valign="Top"><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3" border="0" width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Reconstructed OoW Songlist<a name="70744"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 8 04 1:39 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I'm sure as many of you know, before OoW came out, we were told
<br />
that the songs on lucy were just placeholders, and that by the 
<br />
time OoW would come out, we would have lots of new songs as
<br />
well.  Then OoW came out and every song that was a placeholder
<br />
actually was our OoW song and it really seems that there should
<br />
have been new songs but that it was somehow left unfinished.
<br />

<br />
Other classes got their spells, and there is a distinctive feel or
<br />
style that OoW brought to new spells.  That style is completely
<br />
absent from bard songs.  Because I have no life, have played a
<br />
bard for over 5 years, and also play other classes at high levels,
<br />
and did I mention I have no life, I decided to take it upon myself
<br />
to attempt to reconstruct a list of OoW songs that would fit the
<br />
style of the expansion a lot more than what we currently got.
<br />

<br />
So here it is, an eqdiva exclusive,
<br />

<br />
Lost List of Songs we should have received in OoW.  
<br />
(all stats shown for lvl 70 player).
<br />

<br />
Lvl 66.  Dirge of Metala
<br />
-reduce movement speed by 52 percent.
<br />
-duration 10 ticks.
<br />
-recast time 12 seconds.  
<br />
-resistance check (-12 Magic)
<br />
-Brass instrument required, only modifies resist check. 
<br />

<br />
Lvl 66.  Bellow of Chaos
<br />
-Stun (2.00 Seconds)  (max lvl 73)
<br />
-Silence for 3 ticks (cannot silence unmezzable)
<br />
-recast time 2 minutes.
<br />
-Singing based, modifies stun duration.
<br />

<br />
Lvl 67   Call of the Tradewinds
<br />
-increase agility by 50.
<br />
-increase agility cap by 25.
<br />
-increase Chance to Crit 2% (beneficial spells only)
<br />
-duration 3 ticks.
<br />
-Wind Instrument based, will modify all stats, but not required.
<br />

<br />
Lvl 67 Cantata of Life  (group version)
<br />
-Increase hit points by 45 per tick.
<br />
-Increase Mana by 25 per tick.
<br />
-duration 3 ticks.
<br />
-String Instrument based (modifies hp regen only), 
<br />
but not required.
<br />

<br />
Lvl 68   War March of Muram
<br />
-increase attack speed by 64 percent.
<br />
-increase strength by 73.
<br />
-increase strength cap by 30.  (stacks with wunshi)
<br />
-increase attack by 38.
<br />
-increase damage shield by 23.
<br />
-Brass Instrument based(will modify all but haste), 
<br />
but not required.
<br />

<br />
Lvl 68   Yelhun's Mystic Silence
<br />
-decrease all resistance by 25.
<br />
-duration 7 ticks.
<br />
-recast time 12 seconds.
<br />
-resistance check (-1000 Magic)
<br />
-Percussion instrument required, modifies. 
<br />
(does not stack with OoS nor HoS)
<br />

<br />
Lvl 69 Verse of Vesagran
<br />
-Mitigate melee damage by 3%, 400 total
<br />
-Mitigate spell damage by 5%, 600 total
<br />
-Increase Stats by 12 (over cap, stacks with all)
<br />
-Wind Instrument required, modifies everything.
<br />
-Recast time 12 seconds.
<br />

<br />
Lvl 69 Chorus of Life  (AE version)
<br />
-Increase hit points by 45 per tick.
<br />
-Increase Mana by 25 per tick.
<br />
-duration 3 ticks.
<br />
-String Instrument based (modifies hp regen only), 
<br />
but not required.
<br />

<br />
Lvl 70 Lost Composition of Vesagran
<br />
-increase all resistance by 50.
<br />
-increase all resistance caps by 50.
<br />
-Area Effect Song, Percussion instrument based, 
<br />
but not required, modifies.
<br />
(stacks with other 2 AE resists songs but is blocked 
<br />
by Psalm of Veeshan, and will block Guardian Rythmns.)
<br />

<br />
Lvl 70 Vulka's Lullaby
<br />
-Mesmerize (2/73)
<br />
-duration 4 ticks.
<br />
-resistance check (-12 Magic)
<br />
-Singing based, modifies resistance check.
<br />
-range 200.
<br />

<br />
Ancient lvl 70 Ancient Call of Power
<br />
-Increase Spell Damage by 30%
<br />
-Increase Haste v3 by 30%
<br />
-Increase Chance to crit 2%  (Detrimental Spell and 
<br />
melee only, stacks with all)
<br />
-Singing based, only modifies chance to crit.
<br />

<br />
If Sony just didn't have a bard guy to come up with ideas, here's
<br />
a bunch of them that are in theme with that other classes got.
<br />

<br />
Comments, flames, arguments, are all welcomed,
<br />
even if it's just to say &quot;I agree&quot;,
<br />

<br />
'Stuce</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%">[link=www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=602255][image noborder]http://www.ichuu.com/Tomonari/pics/Astuceubersig.gif[/image][/link][br][link=www.ichuu.com/Tomonari/][image noborder]http://www.ichuu.com/Tomonari/pics/eottag.gif[/image][/link]
